Package org.eclipse.mat.snapshot

Class MultiplePathsFromGCRootsRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mat.snapshot.MultiplePathsFromGCRootsRecord
  • public class MultiplePathsFromGCRootsRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a set of paths from the GC roots to different objects, which go through one and the same object.

      • nextLevel

        public MultiplePathsFromGCRootsRecord[] nextLevel()
        Returns the next level of the paths. For all paths going through this object the next objects in the paths are taken and grouped again (i.e. the lenght of the returned array will be equal to the number of different objects at the next depth level of the paths). The direction is from the GC roots to the objects
        Returns:
        MultiplePathsFromGCRootsRecord[] Each record in the result represents again paths going through one and the same object
